   <tbody> 
    <tr> 
     <th style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"> <h2>Golden Vow (Spell)</h2> </th> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"><img style="width: 200px; height: 200px;" title="Golden Vow" src="/file/Elden-Ring/golden_vow_incantation_elden_ring_wiki_guide_200px.png" alt="golden vow incantation elden ring wiki guide 200px" width="200" height="200"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>Spell Type</td> 
     <td><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Erdtree Incantations" href="/Erdtree+Incantations" target="">Erdtree Incantations</a></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>FP Cost 47</td> 
     <td>Slots Used: 1</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td colspan="2"><img title="item_effect_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/item_effects_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_55px_18px.png" alt="item effects icon elden ring wiki guide 55px 18px" width="18" height="18">Effect 
      <div class="lineleft">
        Increases attack and defense for self and allies 
      </div> <br><img style="float: left;" title="Attributes Requirement" src="/file/Elden-Ring/attributes-required-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="attributes required elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18">Requires 
      <div class="lineleft"> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Intelligence" href="/Intelligence" target="">Intelligence</a> 0 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Faith" href="/Faith" target="">Faith</a> 25 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Arcane" href="/Arcane" target="">Arcane</a>&nbsp;0 
      </div> </td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Golden Vow (Spell) </strong> is an <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Incantations" href="/Incantations" target="">Incantation</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. Golden Vow provides a buff that increases the attack and defense of your character as well as allies. The buff lasts 80 seconds.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>An incantation of Erdtree Worship.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Increases attack power and defense for the caster and nearby allies.</em><br><em>Hold to continue praying and delay activation.</em></p> 
 <p><em>This incantation has been taught to knights of the royal capital for</em><em> generations, and knights sent on distant expeditions lean on it as a</em><em> source of courage.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Golden Vow (Spell)</h3> 
<p>Where to find Golden Vow (Spell):</p> 
<ul> 
 <li><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Corpse-Stench Shack" href="/Corpse-Stench+Shack">Corpse-Stench Shack</a>, in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Mt Gelmir" href="/Mt+Gelmir">Mt Gelmir</a>. [<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=3403&amp;lat=-82.328125&amp;lng=73.152163&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA" href="/Interactive+Map?id=3403&amp;lat=-82.328125&amp;lng=73.152163&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA">Map link</a>]</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Golden Vow (Spell) Guide</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Stamina Cost: 50.</li> 
 <li>Duration:&nbsp;80 seconds (104 with <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Old Lord's Talisman" href="/Old+Lord's+Talisman">Old Lord's Talisman</a>).</li> 
 <li>Damage +15% (7.5% in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring PvP" href="/PvP" target="">PvP</a>).</li> 
 <li>All Damage Negation +10% (5% in PvP).</li> 
 <li>Damage stacks multiplicatively with&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Flame Grant me Strength" href="/Flame+Grant+me+Strength">Flame, Grant me Strength</a>.</li> 
 <li>Damage reduction component stacks multiplicatively with&nbsp;food buffs such as <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Boiled Crab" href="/Boiled+Crab">Boiled Crab.</a></li> 
 <li>This is an&nbsp;<strong>Aura Buff</strong>&nbsp;and will not&nbsp;stack with other buffs of the same type. 
  <ul> 
   <li>See&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Buffs and Debuffs" href="/Buffs+and+Debuffs" target="">Buffs and Debuffs</a>&nbsp;for more information on stacking buffs.</li> 
  </ul> </li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
